{"tid":1698524,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［提防界票黨］土瓜灣馬沆涌出現「反佔中」素人！！！","createTime":"2019-11-07T14:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T07:19:56.000Z","uid":310311,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b49fa34bdaaea3419c0a374819d4bc27fc213e9c","tid":1698524,"uid":310311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"是咁的，馬沆涌本來係黎廣偉（民主黨，現任區議員）對鄧巧彤（工聯會+禮義廉）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但臨完報名前一日竟然出現一個打住五大訴求既素人⋯⋯？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzJftHJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzJftHJ.png&h=aace9e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MbUqQV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMbUqQV4.jpg&h=003f7445&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6NLEVnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6NLEVnL.jpg&h=8d2e1286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先唔講你張野係零實際政綱（我唔係好明咩叫「抗爭」的手法，陳生見到既話可唔可以解釋下）<br />\n然後我都唔講你無視民動認可左既現任民主黨區議員黎廣偉，直接玩空降落黎報名<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係呢句</span></span><br />\n「和理非沒有帶來改變，只有勇武帶來希望」<br />\n當我都我唔講呢句野啱唔啱，我只問你一個問題<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非無用，咁點解你要黎選區議員唔去前線？？？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啱今日有路過市民係欣榮花園見到佢街站<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁難得見到就聽聽佢講咩啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/7683893167/permalink/10157576116788168?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F7683893167%2Fpermalink%2F10157576116788168%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=674a5b29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/7683893167/permalink/10157576116788168?sfns=mo</a>（唔知有冇預覽，無可以自己入去睇，好短架咋）<br />\n「我地反佔中⋯⋯」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咦？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>「反佔中」？</strong></span></span><br />\n陳生咁勇武咁前排，點解搞錯左做反佔中，仲要loop咁多次先改既？<br />\n大佬啊，先唔講我係呢頭咁耐未見過你啦，你自己都反送中同反佔中都搞錯，選你入去你會唔會將趕走旅行團講成歡迎旅行團架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳曉威先生，我唔知你係咪真手足啦（雖然我嚴重質疑你唔係，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">單單係分化和勇又要選區選呢樣野已經極可疑</span></span>），但就算你係真手足，我都勸你返去做多少少功課再出黎，如果唔係你完全係做緊界票黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27dd70336334c22e8d021e5fe37f1a6c5059404","tid":1698524,"uid":310311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出完po發現打錯「坑」做「沆」，自膠"},{"pid":"ba16677a426a819632414b1061a9f3ee3d421779","tid":1698524,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"推比土瓜灣手足睇"},{"pid":"c76470d2925515d0a1712a3559b4e5fee12b8a2e","tid":1698524,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:22:45.000Z","msg":"點解港共搞個選舉都要搞到咁肉酸"},{"pid":"416eefbeecf2c14ec8682acc9731f9275e5da720","tid":1698524,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:26:23.000Z","msg":"冇人識佢"},{"pid":"8bb227ab8d739b85f3c23aabd0c8435ab402902d","tid":1698524,"uid":310311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌仔不能自推,請大家幫幫手推俾土瓜灣手足睇"},{"pid":"1c6a9d0297a7c0bb9ad1c73d01964e0c19272aa4","tid":1698524,"uid":157491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2ae32e94b8fcb3de131582ec61628288a7f1d200","tid":1698524,"uid":140793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca3387c16dd34bedf35487ea88c7f889c0774b7c","tid":1698524,"uid":116509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:48:35.000Z","msg":"推，好神奇地九龍城有幾區都係咁樣，證明連建制基地班藍屍都驚<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要提醒街坊唔好投𠝹票黨<br />\n<br />\n甴曱近平 曱甴王 習近平"},{"pid":"d7c06bd2dd58e25b2bd7310b7de47954acfbc491","tid":1698524,"uid":89659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"4faaf180086a4fe64ab2d694c223fd836dff30df","tid":1698524,"uid":216760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:49:28.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣選民小心手上一票"},{"pid":"22d2ef0a90412ae929fcb39f317ca5167d8e28f2","tid":1698524,"uid":40,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87e6fdbca0f2c333f71bdd68806e1d5d7300469","tid":1698524,"uid":69194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:12:47.000Z","msg":"反佔中jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44951f15ca75e2fe06afc08070f2defa1582f8c7","tid":1698524,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:15:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"522fd2e31610be7a08225343fc807327571261df","tid":1698524,"uid":184379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:16:21.000Z","msg":"似混水摸魚"},{"pid":"b91e28542644f97c2ef346c7c66050d09e2bd1ae","tid":1698524,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:28:33.000Z","msg":"請廣傳📣📣📣📣📣<br />\n<br />\n唔止美國，依家啲三濫行為，應該受所有民主國家一齊招呼，定義為恐怖主義，等呢啲過街🐭，返晒大灣區啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/L8grMdKB5h\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FL8grMdKB5h&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=6023cf26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/L8grMdKB5h</a>"},{"pid":